      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence. This vehicle has been maintained to a high standard, offering a seamless blend of performance and reliability. Its refined aesthetic and mechanical integrity ensure a superior driving experience for the discerning owner. A premier choice for those seeking quality without compromise.",
      "price": 36500.0,
