    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape for its next adventure. Everything runs smoothly, and it\u2019s been well-loved over the years. I\u2019m super excited to get this into the hands of someone who will enjoy it as much as I have, so I've priced it to be a total steal! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019m happy to chat and tell you all about it!",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW's high-revving masterpiece. Powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system (recently serviced), it delivers linear power through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement and upgraded bushings to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. Performance is managed by a factory limited-slip differential and a tuned MacPherson strut/multi-link suspension setup. The car exhibits honest wear consistent with a well-maintained driver, offering a visceral, analog experience with a 7,900 RPM redline.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Used sedan. Good condition. Clean title. Maintenance up to date. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 30000.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a wonderful example of a well-cared-for daily driver that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a beautiful shine, with only minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with responsible ownership. Inside, the cabin remains smoke-free and inviting; the seats are supportive and free of significant wear, while all power accessories, including the infotainment system and climate control, operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts precisely, backed by a consistent maintenance history and a recent multi-point inspection. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes feel firm and responsive. If you are looking for a dependable, attractive vehicle that is ready to hit the road today without needing immediate investment, this car is an excellent choice.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
